AppSec Roadmap (Zero to Hero)
│
├── 1. Fundamentals of Security
│   ├── Basic Security Concepts
│   │   ├── CIA Triad (Confidentiality, Integrity, Availability)
│   │   ├── Authentication vs. Authorization
│   │   └── Encryption (Symmetric, Asymmetric)
│   └── Networking Basics
│       ├── TCP/IP, DNS, HTTPS
│       ├── HTTP Methods and Status Codes
│       └── SSL/TLS and Certificates
│
├── 2. Programming Knowledge
│   ├── Secure Coding Practices
│   │   └── OWASP Top 10 Security Vulnerabilities
│   ├── Languages
│   │   ├── Python
│   │   ├── JavaScript (Node.js)
│   │   └── Java/.NET (Common Enterprise Languages)
│   ├── Web Development Basics
│   │   ├── HTTP/HTTPS Protocols
│   │   └── Frontend/Backend Interactions (REST, API)
│   └── Secure Code Reviews
│
├── 3. OWASP Top 10
│   ├── Injection Attacks (SQLi, NoSQLi, XSS)
│   ├── Broken Authentication
│   ├── Sensitive Data Exposure
│   ├── XML External Entities (XXE)
│   ├── Broken Access Control
│   ├── Security Misconfiguration
│   ├── Cross-Site Scripting (XSS)
│   ├── Insecure Deserialization
│   └── Insufficient Logging & Monitoring
│
├── 4. Threat Modeling and Secure Design
│   ├── STRIDE Threat Model
│   ├── Data Flow Diagrams (DFDs)
│   ├── Attack Trees
│   ├── Abuse Cases
│   └── Security by Design Principles
│
├── 5. Application Security Testing
│   ├── Static Application Security Testing (SAST)
│   │   └── Tools: SonarQube, Checkmarx, Fortify
│   ├── Dynamic Application Security Testing (DAST)
│   │   └── Tools: OWASP ZAP, Burp Suite, Veracode
│   ├── Interactive Application Security Testing (IAST)
│   │   └── Tools: Contrast Security
│   └── Software Composition Analysis (SCA)
│       └── Tools: Snyk, WhiteSource, OWASP Dependency-Check
│
├── 6. Secure Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC)
│   ├── Security in Agile and DevOps
│   ├── Shift-Left Security
│   ├── Security Requirements in SDLC
│   ├── CI/CD Security Integration
│   └── Security Automation in Pipelines
│
├── 7. Identity and Access Management (IAM)
│   ├── OAuth 2.0
│   ├── OpenID Connect (OIDC)
│   ├── SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language)
│   └── Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
│
├── 8. Secure APIs
│   ├── OWASP API Security Top 10
│   ├── Securing REST APIs
│   └── OAuth, JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
│
├── 9. Mobile Security
│   ├── OWASP Mobile Top 10
│   ├── iOS Security
│   ├── Android Security
│   └── Mobile App Penetration Testing
│
├── 10. Web Application Penetration Testing
│   ├── Reconnaissance (Subdomains, IPs)
│   ├── Exploiting Injection Attacks
│   ├── File Upload and Inclusion Attacks
│   ├── Exploiting Broken Access Controls
│   └── Tools: Burp Suite, OWASP ZAP, Nmap
│
└── 11. Soft Skills and Communication
    ├── Collaborating with Developers
    ├── Writing Secure Coding Guidelines
    └── Incident Handling and Root Cause Analysis
